{
  "stem": "24242.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The fighting group one, and women and children in the other one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was orders by the-- from the higher Russian command.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they should divide the women and children, and have a fighting group, and go out and fight the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not far one from the other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not far.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like 5 kilometers, 10 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes they work together for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then, towards the end of-- in the middle of '43, when we went to [NON-ENGLISH], there already, we work together, the fighting and the--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because over here, in our area where we originated, where we were born and brought up, they attacked us more often-- more often, so we had to look for bigger areas.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you come to a [NON-ENGLISH], this is like endless woods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are places there which a human being was not there yet, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although I think it was in '44 that they attacked us even there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole Nazi army attacked us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, differently because over there, you had a lot of room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't have as much fear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You did not have to be so quiet, like at first, in the smaller woods, where we were born and brought up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here were no villages close by, and those were endless, miles and miles worth of woods that-- that a human being was not there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you cross a little island, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] as I said, there was no-- there was miles of woods, endless--",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
